'''Slavic folklore''' encompasses the [[folklore]] of the [[Slavic peoples]] from their earliest records until today. Folklorists have published a variety of works focused specifically on the topic over the years.<ref name="KONONENKO-2007">See, for example, Kononenko 2007.</ref>

